{"tid":817162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那潮流自殺方法】繼華山後　峨眉山金頂再有人自殺　男子濃霧中跳下捨身崖","createTime":"2018-09-13T08:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T08:52:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"394d3e28ddc94f7c90a2650f6c408ba39fbcb4a5","tid":817162,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DXEP_hOlsLE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDXEP_hOlsLE&d=WVyOaNXIWL2IgPE2XxITITA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7f0385f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DXEP_hOlsLE</a><br />\n繼華山長棧道、峨眉山金頂捨身崖接連兩名男女跳崖自殺後，內地周三（12日）傳出再有同類事件發生，有片段拍到捨身崖上有一道人影從高處跳下，恐怕凶多吉少。<br />\n<br />\n從片段所見，捨身崖上非常大霧，但隱約可見到遠處崖頂上有一道人影，隨後就突然向下跳，並完全消失在濃霧之中，生死不明。附近遊客發現後，傳來陣陣驚呼聲。據網上消息指，跳崖者為一名男子，其自行翻越護欄後跳崖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n有內地傳媒表示，事發後景區立即啟動搜救工作，目前男子的身份仍在核實中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1854520/org/37ad96da0ef7c0669cb9c946a1e0b6eb.jpg/ap-pBdZq5XJmhnQampixlOXOlaWwS2A7udS9SrnUvUo?v=w1440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1854520%2Forg%2F37ad96da0ef7c0669cb9c946a1e0b6eb.jpg%2Fap-pBdZq5XJmhnQampixlOXOlaWwS2A7udS9SrnUvUo%3Fv%3Dw1440&d=WVyOaNXIWL2IgPE2XxITITA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=60672718\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1854520/org/37ad96da0ef7c0669cb9c946a1e0b6eb.jpg/ap-pBdZq5XJmhnQampixlOXOlaWwS2A7udS9SrnUvUo?v=w1440</a><br />\n峨眉金頂捨身崖。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n據了解，峨眉山金頂捨身崖地勢突出，下方峭壁毫無遮攔，可直達700多米深的崖底，故是跳崖自殺的「熱門」區域。有見及此，峨眉區景區早在該處設置密集的防護措施，沿途不但全程均有鋼欄石柱包圍崖邊，且每隔數米便設有中英文對照的警示牌，寫有「珍愛生命，請勿翻越」。<br />\n峨眉山金頂月初有女子跳崖自殺。（影片截圖）<br />\n華山長棧道在7月時有一名男遊客自解安全繩後蹤身躍下萬丈深淵。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n內地近月頻傳跳崖先殺事件，被譽為「華山第一天險」的華山長棧道先是在7月底有一名男性遊客，在眾目睽睽下自行解開安全繩，隨後就突然張開雙臂，縱身躍下逾2000米深的山崖，最終證實死亡；峨眉金頂捨身崖月初亦有一名女子，她未有理會其他遊客勸告，當眾跳崖自殺。女子生前留有一封遺書，自述一直深受抑鬱症困擾。"},{"pid":"c92dcb6352d1dc0cb6c7df5ed91f02b0031ae224","tid":817162,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"上次華山<br />\n今次峨眉<br />\n<br />\n下次 少林 定 武當？"},{"pid":"05a28d9a26c616577ddb01a76ad0b06fec2cb949","tid":817162,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"死得好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44fa2505ce0fd9f31bb17446825e4378c67ffbb","tid":817162,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"2000米CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc16957450fb01349469e01104ae4e8ff56d715c","tid":817162,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"去搵小龍女，唔洗大驚小怪"},{"pid":"90572bcfd443ef1a763d8f225eba24b5bad57538","tid":817162,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2ce66d8acc697310e2c41c9615e315c9a7ce7e7","tid":817162,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc16957450fb01349469e01104ae4e8ff56d715c","tid":817162,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"去搵小龍女，唔洗大驚小怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"滅絕師太"},{"pid":"64c3b6e1b3269fe14f16662d101e866c9a3adcc1","tid":817162,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"拍片質素有改善喎 終於唔係480p個fd"},{"pid":"39c22c92ed232ba06a2ada40faa3b6fd5b6a424d","tid":817162,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"諗起臥虎藏龍套戲"},{"pid":"4aca00624d55e409b8540e725c1404b80cfeda87","tid":817162,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90572bcfd443ef1a763d8f225eba24b5bad57538","tid":817162,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"ching 帶頭型畀我地睇 <img src=\"/assets/fac